(59914, 24433, 0, 1, 'The Poet 練團室版本', '', '2013-01-30 00:00:00', 2000, 0, 2, 7, 'There’s a shepherd under the shade of a tree   在那兒的樹陰下有個牧羊人\r\nHis sheep are not far from the flowing stream   他的羊群在小溪不遠處\r\nA ragged cloak swings the Northern wind   北風中飄盪著破舊的斗篷\r\nPlays the duet with the flute, a sorrow filled   像是和牧羊人之笛合奏著雙簧，充滿了悲傷\r\n\r\nThere’s a man who walks alone beside the stream   有個人沿著小溪走了過來\r\nHe wipes his dusty glasses and wipes again   他擦了又擦那副骯髒的眼鏡\r\nKeeps searching for that lost fountain pen   不斷尋找他遺失的鋼筆\r\nUsed to write an endless pain, with lovely phrases   用美麗的詞彙書寫無盡的痛苦\r\n\r\nPoured my heart, poured my mind   我窮盡了一切\r\nAin’t no daylight I could describe   要敘說的不是那陽光普照\r\nNot the night, or moonlight   不是那黑夜，也不是那月光\r\nBut the artist’s saintly pride   而是作家崇高的自尊\r\nLet the blank filled with black   讓墨水填滿這張空白\r\nLeft a reason that I lived, perhaps   或許能讓我有個曾經活過的理由\r\nTime passed by, things remain   時光飛逝，景物依舊\r\nHow do you remember my name?   你要如何記得我的名字呢?\r\n\r\nThere’s a shining object lies nearby the tree   樹旁有著閃閃發光的物品\r\nThe whistling stopped and music disappeared   笛聲停止音樂也跟著消失\r\nThe shepherd found that artist’s fountain pen   牧羊人發現了作家遺失的鋼筆\r\nWould make out another pieces, not the end   也許能在寫出下一部作品，還尚未結束\r\n\r\nPoured my heart, poured my mind   我窮盡了一切\r\nAin’t no daylight I could describe   要敘說的不是那陽光普照\r\nNot the night, or moonlight   不是那黑夜，也不是那月光\r\nBut the artist’s saintly pride   而是作家崇高的自尊\r\nLet the blank filled with black   讓墨水填滿這張空白\r\nLeft a reason that I lived, perhaps   或許能讓我有個曾經活過的理由\r\nTime passed by, things remain   時光飛逝，景物依舊\r\nHow do you remember my name?   你要如何記得我的名字呢?\r\nTime passed by, things remain   時光飛逝，景物依舊\r\nHow do you remember my name?   你要如何記得我的名字呢?\r\n', '', 249, '', 'Vank', 'Vank', 'NeverMind', '', '', 0, 0, 1, '2013-01-30 00:41:55', '2013-10-07 17:23:48', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
